href="marcelofiore.xml"
addr="marcelofiore"
title="Marcelo Fiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Any <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00I7.xml"
addr="jms-00I7"
title="Relation">relation</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00KF.xml"
addr="jms-00KF"
title="Function">function</fr:link> if and only if for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>, there exists some unique <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\mathrel {R}b]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
