display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>, we have <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathord {\#}{\mathopen {}\left (A\mathbin {\rightharpoonup } B\right )\mathclose {}}={\mathopen {}\left (\mathord {\#}{B}+1\right )\mathclose {}}^{\mathord {\#}{A}}]]></fr:tex>, recalling that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathord {\#}{S}]]></fr:tex> is the cardinality of a set <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
