text="Functions are uniquely-valued relations"><fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00KF.xml"
addr="jms-00KF"
title="Function">Functions</fr:link> are uniquely-valued <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00I7.xml"
addr="jms-00I7"
title="Relation">relations</fr:link></fr:title><fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>22</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
type="local"
href="jonmsterling.xml"
addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author><fr:contributor><fr:link
type="local"
href="marcelofiore.xml"
addr="marcelofiore"
title="Marcelo Fiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Any <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00I7.xml"
addr="jms-00I7"
title="Relation">relation</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00KF.xml"
addr="jms-00KF"
title="Function">function</fr:link> if and only if for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>, there exists some unique <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\mathrel {R}b]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
toc="false"
numbered="true"
